  "title": "*Temp Junior Medical Laboratory Technologist (6months) *#HHLT",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: Novena</p><p>📅 Contract: Feb – Sep 2026</p><p>💰 Salary: Up to $2,500/month<br /><br /></p><p>⏰ Working Hours</p><p>Mon–Thu: 8.30am – 6.00pm</p><p>Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm<br /><br /></p><p>🧬 Job Scope</p><p>Support daily lab operations: specimen collection, processing & data recording</p><p>Operate lab equipment; perform QC, calibration & basic troubleshooting</p><p>Handle requests for specimen info, lab results & lab materials</p><p>Assist with laboratory equipment maintenance</p><p>Ensure compliance with lab safety & regulatory requirements</p><p>Support research, education or clinical improvement activities when required<br /><br /></p><p>✅ Requirements</p><p>Minimum Diploma in Biomedical Science or equivalent</p><p>At least 1 year of lab experience preferred</p><p>Vaccinated Tdap / MMR / Covid / Varicella (VZV) / Hep B<br /><br /><br />If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
